ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectEdmundston Chamber of Commerce (New Brunswick) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the EDMUNDSTON CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in New Brunswick, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the Town of Edmundston to the City of Edmundston including the communities of St-Jacques, St-Basile and Verret.
